title: #92Noon! Montage/Bercich/Russo/Cronin/JG
description: Montage starts a victory Monday show! Bercich in studio, Russo checks in from Nashville ahead of tonight's Wild/Preds tilt, Courtney Cronin then in studio for more NFL/Vikings opinions and JG looks back at Saturday's Gophers game in Columbus!
